paragraph_01: frisbeegolfrata.info is a hobby project and it is "work in progress". The idea behind the service is to help disc golfers to easily find great courses from Finland.
paragraph_02: The website data is updated automatically so if you find any errors or omissions, please let me know "janne [AT] malluusenfrisbeegolfrata.fi". Also send a message if you have new features in mind that you think the service needs.
paragraph_03: Thanks to the frisbeegolfradat.fi and discgolfmetrix.com services from which site data is retrieved. And thank you for using this service!
